  <name>Minecraft Server Manager</name>
  <summary>Manage Minecraft servers with ease</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Minecraft Server Manager is a comprehensive GTK-based application designed to simplify the management of Minecraft servers, providing an intuitive interface for server administration.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Easy server creation and management</li>
      <li>Plugin and mod management with Modrinth integration</li>
      <li>Server console with colorized output</li>
      <li>Configuration file editor for server settings</li>
      <li>Support for Bukkit, Spigot, Paper, and other server types</li>
      <li>Download and install plugins/mods directly from Modrinth</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
